  "description": "An ordinal λ that bounds the settling index of a family of predication valuations: settling steps τ range over τ \u003c λ. Typically ω (countable settlings) but may be any fixed ordinal, supporting transfinite settlings while avoiding the size-theoretic issues of indexing by the class of all ordinals.",
